node.text:
Rookies aren't supposed to soar as high as @itsjust_morgan has on the CT in 2021. While the surf punditry waited for him to fly too close to the sun, event after event he just kept shining brighter.
Follow Morgan's rise to the #ripcurlwslfinals, link in bio. 🏆 @ripcurl_usa

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by World Surf League on August 31, 2021 tagging @itsjust_morgan. May be an image of 2 people, outdoors and text that says 'World Worldo.5 No.5 No. MORGAN RIP CURL WORLD SURF LEAGUE FINALS WSL SEPTEMBER 9-17, 2021 WATCH ON WORLDSURFLEAGUE.COM CIBILIC'.

node.text: Will @itsjust_morgan be the first rookie to win a Men’s World Title? Follow Morgan’s rise to the #ripcurlwslfinals, link in bio. 🏆 @ripcurl_usa

May be an image of 10 people and text that says 'RIP CURL WSL FINALS WrldNo.1 CARISSA MOORE WorldNo.1 GABRIEL MEDINA WdNo. TATIANA WESTON-WEBB WorldNo. ÍTALO FERREIRA WNo.3 World SALLY FITZGIBBONS World FILIPE TOLEDO WorldNo.4 STEPHANIE GILMORE RIPCURL WorldNo. CONNER COFFIN World No. JOHANNE DEFAY WldNo. MORGAN CIBILIC'.
